videos.headline: Brown receives Sam Foltz scholarship
videos.description: Prior to the game, Nebraska place kicker Drew Brown is awarded the Sam Foltz scholarship, in memory of fellow Huskers kicker Sam Foltz who tragically died in an automobile accident.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown receives Sam Foltz scholarship) 2016/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Moore goes deep for TD to increases Nebraska's lead
videos.description: To kick off the fourth quarter, Nebraska QB Tommy Armstrong Jr. makes the pass to WR Alonzo Moore for a 57-yard touchdown, putting the Cornhuskers up 28-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moore goes deep for TD to increases Nebraska’s lead) 2016/09/03 ESHEET
